edu.wpi.cs.jburge.SEURAT.editors
Class SelectType

java.lang.Object
  edu.wpi.cs.jburge.SEURAT.editors.SelectType

public class SelectType
extends java.lang.Object

Presents the user with a list of rationale elements of a specific type to select from. The user also has the option of searching for an element in the list and can add new items.

Author:
jburge
